data.content:
Implemented and pushed to origin/main in commit 69ecbe66.

Changed scripts/release.sh to:
- require attached target branch, clean worktree, and configured upstream;
- fetch upstream + tags before version calculation;
- fail dry-runs before mutation when the branch is behind;
- fast-forward a clean behind branch for real releases before gates;
- run final release quality gates inside the script;
- publish branch and tag with one atomic push;
- on push races, fetch, rebase, retag, rerun gates, and retry.

Changed .agents/skills/ship-release/SKILL.md to require main sync before preview/gates and to document the script-owned final safety path.

Verification passed: bash -n, shellcheck, targeted temporary git race simulation, clean release dry-run, bun run lint, bunx tsc --noEmit, bun run test, bun run build.
